        "RouteSubjects": "<p>You can do a degree in <a href=\"https://www.hca.ac.uk/course/artist-blacksmithing\">artist blacksmithing</a> from Hereford College of Arts.</p>",
        "FurtherRouteInformation": "<p>You'll need a portfolio of your work and creative ideas for course interviews.</p>",
        "RouteRequirement": "You'll usually need:"
      },
      {
