            "Text": "equivalent entry requirements"
          },
          {
            "Id": "aedbc62b-5024-47ae-8447-3ce762e6238b",
            "Title": "Show Apprenticeship Guide",
            "Url": "https://www.gov.uk/apprenticeships-guide",
            "Text": "guide to apprenticeships"
          }
        ],
        "RouteSubjects": "<p>You can get into industrial blacksmithing through an engineering or welding intermediate or advanced apprenticeship. </p>\n<p>You may be able to use this to find a trainee job with a specialist metalwork company.</p>",
        "FurtherRouteInformation": "",
        "RouteRequirement": "You'll usually need:"
      }
    ],
    "FurtherInformation": {
      "CareerTips": "<p>You'll need to show examples of your work and decorative ideas to get onto a design-related course or if contacting blacksmiths about trainee positions.</p>",
      "ProfessionalAndIndustryBodies": "<p>You could join the <a href=\"https://www.babamembers.org.uk/baba-membership/\">British Artist Blacksmiths Association</a> and <a href=\"https://blacksmithscompany.co.uk/the-company/joining/\">The Worshipful Company of Blacksmiths</a> for professional development and to make industry contacts.</p>",
      "FurtherInformation": "<p>You can get more details about working as an artist blacksmith from the <a href=\"http://www.baba.org.uk/education-training-and-courses/\">British Artist Blacksmiths Association</a> and <a href=\"https://ccskills.org.uk/careers/advice/article/an-artist-blacksmith-career\">Creative Choices</a>.</p>"
    },
    "FurtherRoutes": {
      "Work": "<p>You could work as an assistant to an experienced blacksmith and learn the craft on the job. Experience in metalwork and technical drawing can be useful for this career.</p>",
      "Volunteering": "",
      "DirectApplication": "",
      "OtherRoutes": "<p>You'll find it useful to do a short course in blacksmithing. This will help you decide if it's a suitable career and may be useful if you plan to look for a training position. The <a href=\"https://www.babamembers.org.uk/baba-directory/\">British Artist Blacksmiths Association</a> has details of training organisations.</p>"
    },
    "IntroText": "<p>You can get into this job through:</p>\n<ul>\n    <li>a university course</li>\n    <li>a college course</li>\n    <li>an apprenticeship</li>\n    <li>working towards this role</li>\n    <li>specialist courses run by private training organisations</li>\n</ul>",
    "Registrations": []
  },
  "WhatYouWillDoData": {
    "DailyTasks": "<p>For each job, you'll:</p>\n<ul>\n    <li>sketch out new design plans or follow customer instructions</li>\n    <li>heat metals to the right temperature in a forge or furnace</li>\n    <li>shape metals with hand tools like hammers, punches and anvils</li>\n    <li>use power tools, like drills, lathes and hydraulic presses</li>\n    <li>join metal parts together using riveting and welding methods</li>\n    <li>apply finishes</li>\n</ul>",
